data.description: This immaculate 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom end unit ranch townhome is a true gem. Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting living area, adorned with tasteful decor and ample natural light. The three bedrooms are generously sized. The owner's suite boasts a private en-suite bathroom, creating a serene retreat within your own home. This single-level layout is not only practical but also enhances the sense of openness. Enjoy the convenience of a private patio, perfect for entertaining or simply unwinding after a long day. With meticulous upkeep, this home is move-in ready, offering a rare opportunity to experience the joys of effortless living.
